---
source: tests/parser.rs
expression: "tree(r\"\\cmd[opt]{req}\")"
---
ROOT@0..14
  PARAGRAPH@0..14
    COMMAND@0..14
      CONTROL_WORD@0..4 "\\cmd"
      OPTIONAL@4..9
        L_BRACKET@4..5 "["
        WORD@5..8 "opt"
        R_BRACKET@8..9 "]"
      GROUP@9..14
        L_BRACE@9..10 "{"
        WORD@10..13 "req"
        R_BRACE@13..14 "}"
